original_title: UFC Fight Night 155: de Randamie vs. Ladd
overview: UFC Fight Night 155: de Randamie vs. Ladd was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that was held on July 13, 2019 at Golden 1 Center in Sacramento, California. A women's bantamweight bout between the inaugural UFC Women's Featherweight Champion Germaine de Randamie and Aspen Ladd served as the event headliner.
title: UFC Fight Night 155: de Randamie vs. Ladd
